:"2017-08-04T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬睇醫生果陣 <br />\n記得講你有懷疑佢係lyme disease 既concern <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlyme disease 無咁易中 <br />\n通常要俾隻野咬住10個鍾先會傳染<br />\n同埋主要都係美國東岸多 其他地方無乜<br />\n反而擔心下日本腦炎果d就實際<br />\n<br />\nbtw 一發燒就快d再睇醫生 唔好拖"},{"pid":"86d1ceaba0d085a22f78ad64ba48d218ca981bdb","tid":346661,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722c45a40a86e1f2b2e1b1ce71500ba02bcd430a","tid":346661,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬睇醫生果陣 <br />\n記得講你有懷疑佢係lyme disease 既concern <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要同醫生講去過北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a64219e20393182d6370d624d33232784cd1f6","tid":346661,"uid":17235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>萊姆病<br />\n<br />\n病因<br />\n由蜱傳播的Burgdorferi疏螺旋體為病原體。<br />\n<br />\n病徵<br />\n1、皮膚病變：常為首發症狀，特徵性表現為慢性遊走性紅斑，初起為紅色斑疹或丘疹，逐漸擴大成環殂損害。一般出現在蜱叮咬後3&mdash;32天，好發於軀幹、大腿、腹股溝、腋下等處。<br />\n2、神經系統病變：約見於15%的患者，與皮疹同時或消退後1&mdash;6周出現。表現為腦膜炎、腦神經炎、舞蹈症、小腦共濟失調，出現腦膜刺激征、昏迷、面癱或三叉神經痛等。<br />\n3、心臟病變：見於8%左右的患者，常於皮損出現3周後發生房室傳導阻滯、心肌炎、心包炎或全心炎等。<br />\n4、關節病變：約見於60%的患者，多累及大關節，尤其是膝關節，反覆發作腫脹、疼痛，10%的患者可轉變為慢性關節炎。<br />\n5、其他症狀：發熱、乏力、肌痛、噁心、嘔吐、結膜炎、虹膜炎、淋巴結及陰莖腫大等。<br />\n<br />\nRIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAvril Lavige都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過差啲死姐"},{"pid":"c1cb4e2477e2be0349d0af4fdba723626f15173f","tid":346661,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"絲打唔好死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比我屌埋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c148721658cc1e7a209331047c0a7e20a0026362","tid":346661,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"絲打開埋樣"},{"pid":"3763452db94ac14fc710409041166ee22408c885","tid":346661,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打d腳趾一定好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好臭就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7aa3c30229223e2a26694916c75e6b68a82c7b3","tid":346661,"uid":119555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T21:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/sxga4r1p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsxga4r1p&h=bf43a301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4xbeac6y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4xbeac6y&h=f8a2606c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前排去左北海道唔知俾咩咬到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾個禮拜都唔散，愈發愈大，有冇人知係咩黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你比左隻乳暈蚊咬左。中左乳頭病毒，中毒好深下....."},{"pid":"15bc9924170b053844276b79739b6537e0a31347","tid":346661,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T21:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絲打d腳趾一定好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好臭就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722654c629ecd6efdf782cec3ea81145a3cd09a5","tid":346661,"uid":87646,"like":0,"disli